PROJECT FallRisk
INTENT Detect patient fall risk and notify staff only when risk confidence is high.
MODE risk
ENTITY Patient

FIELDS Patient
  age
  mobility
  medication_load
  previous_falls
  cognitive_state
END

GOAL minimize_fall_incidents
GOAL minimize_false_alerts

CONSTRAINT risk > 0.80
ACTION_THRESHOLD 0.90

ACTION Notify
  POLICY simulate_only
  CALL simulated.nurse_station.alert
END
